==English==
===Noun===
'''projection''' (''plural:'' '''projections''')
# something which [[project]]s, [[protrude]]s, [[jut]]s out, [[stick]]s out, or [[stand]]s out
#:''The face of the cliff had many '''projections''' big enough for birds to nest on.''
# a [[forecast]] or [[prognosis]] obtained by [[extrapolation]]
# {{psychology}} an assumption that others have similar thoughts as oneself

